shot every second for 50 seconds.
Features: Laser sight, optic sight, ruggerized weapon body (to melee
standards), mounting rail for underslung secondary weapon.

Energy	ROF	Dam Dice	Pen	Bulk	Mag	Range
40 kj	SA5	10-5-3-1-1	Nil	6	50	200 (300)
