    'body' => 'About lasers
----
I have to admit that it was a great shock to me when I discovered that
lasers had nil Pen. But then I thought that maybe there is a reason for
that. Don\'t you think that they way lasers do damage is that they burn,
or should I say BOIL tissue? As it is much more easier to get the water
(human cells) to boil than say metal, normal hand-held lasers don\'t have
energy to vaporize (sp?) metal armor.

Yes, I know it would be possible to put more energy to laser beam but then
we have to make them big. In fact in RCEG (RC Equipment Guide) there is
one squad laser that have Pen «! OK I admit that it has ROF of 1/4.
Besides hand-held lasers penetrate all non-metal armor without reducing
a single dice of damage.

