targets, then "blind" them appropriately, for example, using EMP
devices. This is probably necessary if one wants to land troops on the
planet (transports make nice targets). It probably will also have 
bad effects on the planet itself (sensor-blinding weapons probably do 
nasty things to the local technology base), but one has to expect the
enemy to take extreme measures if one has an "unassailable" defense...
