    'from' => 'Rob Miracle rwm@MPGN.COM',
    'body' => '> When I\'m looking at the weapon list, there is this thinggy called "bulk".
>  
> What is it?

It is a value used to resolve initiative ties.

> How do I use it?

If the two combatants have the same initiative, take their agility and
subtract the weapon bulk.  The higher agility (after adjusting for bulk)
goes first.

See Page 265 (in 1.1) First Column, under "Resolving Ties"

Rob


